(In reply to Jayaprakash Arthanareeswaran from comment #2) > Hmm... URLClassLoader#close() is a 1.7 method and the apt.core project is > still at 1.5. More importantly, eclipse needs to run with a 1.6 JRE :(
You can do something like: if (classLoader instanceof Closeable) ((Closeable) classLoader).close();
This would not eliminate the resource leak under JRE 1.6, but under JRE 1.7 the problem would be fixed.
